#inner-work[
  *The Sophie Mercury as Inner Faculty*

  The Mineral Mercury, in the inner work, corresponds to the developed capacity
  for mineral-level perception: the ability to attend to what is happening in
  a sealed mineral preparation with the same sensitivity that was applied to
  a plant in the Year One vigils.

  This capacity does not arise automatically from reading about it. It is built
  through the sustained practice of attentive observation across all three years.
  Reflect: what perceptual capacities have genuinely developed since Year One?
  What do you notice now that you could not have noticed then?
]

